Paper: hep-th/9210026

Date: 1992-10-06

Title: Faddeev-Popov method for anomalous quasigroups

Authors: Jordi Par\'{\i}s

Comments: 13 pages, LaTeX (macros included), UB-ECM-PF 92/24

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B300 (1993) 104-110

A generalization of the Faddeev-Popov procedure to deal with either anomalousand non-anomalous gauge theories with closed, irreducible gauge algebra ispresented. An expression for the Wess-Zumino action is obtained.